divs: Sighting Details5 orange vertical objects gliding at 3000 feet moved in sequence from East to Northwest then disappeared North of Hwy 48 just west of Frederic Wisconsin. We viewed from Round Lake and last one went nearly over our head. The objects were silent, propelled and illuminated in orange. Estimate size that of a roadside pine tree. We saw first one come up over east side of lake then 4 more came in sequence. We did not have a camers.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Frederic
This sighting has never been favorited.
